  "text": "The algorithm used in the local search is based on the one described in the paper [CITATION_1] . It is a trust-region SQO method that makes use of a funnel bound on the infeasibility of the iterates in order to ensure convergence. At each iteration k, we have an iterate (x k , s k ) such that x k ∈ Y k , where Y k defines the interpolation set at iteration k. Every iterate satisfies the following bound constraints:",
